      <title>加拿大公寓市场困境加剧 贷款方转为开发商</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-20/growing-distress-in-canada-condos-turns-lenders-into-developers</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一些向加拿大陷入困境的公寓开发商提供贷款的机构发现，他们别无选择，只能购买他们支持的问题公寓项目并自行完成建设。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-20/growing-distress-in-canada-condos-turns-lenders-into-developers</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 20 Nov 2024 14:00:30 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
